{"tid":388657,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺以為四色定理比人證實左D人好撚ON9","createTime":"2017-09-05T15:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T02:37:38.000Z","uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75294c072c1142ad9523bddc9ee7483f00fbe84c","tid":388657,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"屌那星<br />\n講咁撚耐<br />\n叫班證明左四色定理既撚樣<br />\n比少少論述黎睇下都唔撚得<br />\n根本就未有答案<br />\n是但搵個飛地都秒柒你地班數學家啦<br />\n拎部電腦計黎計去就鳩UP話證明左<br />\n無撚野呀? 計錯數唔撚得?"},{"pid":"f36d4e30c9282231af9e6a57aeadfd5942fd21fd","tid":388657,"uid":34277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ed60714462c60ae6af2f5206c7b303e60d00d1","tid":388657,"uid":68626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇高見呀 哦哦哦 紅掌撥清波?"},{"pid":"abb4d6aecadd1b5b97bf6f3104f3874b0d7fb425","tid":388657,"uid":24547,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"9a24558f12ce01ce16ec15bd6a45a20e386815fe","tid":388657,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:19:40.000Z","msg":"連登D數學家去撚晒邊?"},{"pid":"d2d39f5c206fccffc4f44ad9a0bc94fddb2b896d","tid":388657,"uid":10890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"四色定理本身就係假設冇飛地喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc72d6d98d2e12674f99246e691ca7a964b43b33","tid":388657,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:30:28.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"feda40132f404917c2fa816cd7aa0167fcdb66b6","tid":388657,"uid":60166,"like":0,"di